# lsa-gallery

A minimalist, high-performance image gallery under **Liberty-ShareAlike 1.0 (LSA-1.0)**.

- Full license text: <https://github.com/ShortTimeNoSee/liberty-sharealike/blob/v1.0/LICENSE>
